## Navigation for Admin Pages

### Use DashboardNav, Add Admin Link

```typescript
// app/admin/growth/page.tsx

import DashboardNav from '@/app/components/DashboardNav';

export default function AdminPage() {
  return (
    <>
      <DashboardNav />
      {/* Admin content */}
    </>
  );
}
```

**Future: Add admin link to DashboardNav**

```typescript
// app/components/DashboardNav.tsx

{session?.user?.role === 'admin' && (
  <Link href="/admin/growth" className="...">
    Admin
  </Link>
)}
```

**Why:**
- Reuses existing nav (consistent UX)
- Admin link only visible to admins (role check)
- Admin pages are authenticated pages (not public)

